<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/726791-can-any-one-a-detailed-reference-for-this">Can any one a detailed reference for this quote?
&quot;if we submit everything to reason our religion will be left with nothing mysterious&quot;
Thanks</a>
</div>
