        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3811226226" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7755228964493517961">This bushy and dense work is the last book of Jansenist Blaise Pascal, singing the praises of the Christian religion in the face of non-believers and sceptics in a whole lot of reflections. For my part, this reading was compulsory in the academic baccalaureate program, since I only put two stars, it goes without saying that I did not stick at all to Pascalian ideas.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


